gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 113, Clippers 104
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nuggets defeat the Clippers, 113-104 tonight without Nikola Jokic in the lineup. Reggie Jackson totaled 35 points (15-19 FG), 13 assists, and five rebounds as DeAndre Jordan added 21 points, 13 rebounds, and five assists in the victory. Kawhi Leonard led the Clippers with 31 points and eight rebounds as Ivica Zubac added 23 points and 14 rebounds. The Nuggets improve to 12-6 while the Clippers move to 7-9.
